<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عن عطاء <span class="c2">(قال)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>: لا تباع خدمة <span class="c2">(المدبر)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إلا من نفسه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
